# Placeholder for generated images

This directory stores images generated by scripts in `gen_scripts/`:
- `ch05-segmentation-architectures.gif` - FCN vs U-Net vs DeepLab comparison
- `ch05-iou-calculation.gif` - IoU metric visualization
- `ch05-unet-skip-connections.gif` - U-Net architecture diagram
- `ch05-progress-check.png` - ProductionCV progress dashboard

Images are also generated by notebook execution:
- `ch05-sample-data.png`
- `ch05-training-curves.png`
- `ch05-segmentation-results.png`
- `ch05-per-class-iou.png`
- `ch05-class-imbalance.png`
